      "title": "A Valentine&rsquo;s Day cartoon for New Scientist.",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b466b6fc65c9172af73d2362f9a78ab/5ee37488b9aed9da-a3/s640x960/e045c6e9ec6197f717d3124d489853d4a6907a7a.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"800\" data-orig-width=\"1200\" alt=\" Title: A Valentine&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99;s Day experiment   In an effort to test the efficacy of cupids arrows of desire.  A placebo group is shot with regular arrows.  Their injuries range from moderate to sever.  Unexpectedly, romances struck up in hospital and lawyers&#xE2;&#x80;&#x99; waiting rooms create a &quot;romance ratio&quot; similar to that of magic arrows.  However, once the cost of compensation claims is factored in, it is decided to discontinue the experiment.\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b466b6fc65c9172af73d2362f9a78ab/5ee37488b9aed9da-a3/s75x75_c1/6b3aac8069bc943521ef1bc6218499b03be494bf.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b466b6fc65c9172af73d2362f9a78ab/5ee37488b9aed9da-a3/s100x200/b5e4585d6e852fb37d0d3b6522c669c2c22dd0c6.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b466b6fc65c9172af73d2362f9a78ab/5ee37488b9aed9da-a3/s250x400/55bfa4460da1dd2a713cfd40156cfb62c98255a4.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b466b6fc65c9172af73d2362f9a78ab/5ee37488b9aed9da-a3/s400x600/38be55365f64828b0f3031c5eae081661beae5aa.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b466b6fc65c9172af73d2362f9a78ab/5ee37488b9aed9da-a3/s500x750/129ea987e3f89436941b664e4672b04f0a62bb34.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b466b6fc65c9172af73d2362f9a78ab/5ee37488b9aed9da-a3/s540x810/62cb853591b55913115e721502c4ad37ec6dadfa.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b466b6fc65c9172af73d2362f9a78ab/5ee37488b9aed9da-a3/s640x960/e045c6e9ec6197f717d3124d489853d4a6907a7a.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/9b466b6fc65c9172af73d2362f9a78ab/5ee37488b9aed9da-a3/s1280x1920/aaf80b28882363f40cd1b56697b60568fbdb8635.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/>"
